title: Jews For Jesus (1973)
description:
Jews For Jesus 

Comix JJ, 1973, 36 pages

Illustrated by Steve Gregg

Written by Unsure

There was at least four issues of this comic, is says so in the back, and this is issue number four right here.

This appears inside the front cover. lol...

The stories in this book are straight from the files of Jews For Jesus in Corte Madera California. They were written by Jews, for Jews, not particularly for Christians! If you are a Christian reader and don't like the book, too bad. It wasn't written for you! If you are a Jew and don't like the book, sorry 'bout that!
